  Download, Save, Maximize2, XCircle, ChevronDown, Plus, 
  Trash2, Loader2, Sparkles, Layers, Video, Film,
  Crop, Sliders, Check, RotateCcw, Moon, Sun, AlertCircle,
  ChevronsUp, FileText, Copy, Music, File as FileIcon, FileType,
